BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Spinoff! The One Man Show(girl)
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260709T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260709T213000
DTSTAMP:20260710T043905Z
UID:occ-1655@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Cabaret
DESCRIPTION:One man sings Broadway's leading ladies — a 30-seat lounge c
 abaret\, one drink ticket included\, 21 and up.\n\nClaudio Pestana\, a reg
 ular on Atlanta's musical-theatre stages\, works through the numbers Broad
 way's most celebrated divas made famous\, from classic songbook to modern 
 showstoppers. His local credits include Jersey Boys with City Springs Thea
 tre Company and Assassins at the Jennie T. Anderson Theatre. Presented by 
 The Strand Theatre in a 30-seat lounge setting\, with one drink ticket per
  ticket and the bar open after the show\; guests must be 21 or older.
GEO:33.9536122;-84.5492054
LAST-MODIFIED:20260709T203452Z
LOCATION:The Strand Theatre\, 117 N Park Square
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://thestrand.my.salesforce-sites.com/ticket/#/instances/a0FPs0000
 07EtgXMAS
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Jukebox Giants: Disco Fever!
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260710T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260710T220000
DTSTAMP:20260710T043905Z
UID:occ-918@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Cabaret
DESCRIPTION:A song-and-dance revue of disco hits — Donna Summer\, Bee Ge
 es\, and ABBA covers with a live band.\n\nA revue of 1970s disco hits\, wi
 th singers and dancers backed by a live band working through songs made fa
 mous by Donna Summer\, the Bee Gees\, ABBA\, and others. Expect sequins\, 
 choreography\, and a crowd on its feet by the second number. Presented by 
 the Strand Theatre. Note: the production may include flashing lights.
GEO:33.9536122;-84.5492054
LAST-MODIFIED:20260710T043458Z
LOCATION:The Strand Theatre\, 117 N Park Square
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://thestrand.my.salesforce-sites.com/ticket/#/instances/a0FPs0000
 06IR4jMAG
END:VEVENT
